<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; color: #000; line-height: 1.5; padding: 50px; }
        .header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 40px; }
        .title { font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: underline; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .date { text-align: right; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .recipient { margin-bottom: 30px; }
        .subject { font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 30px; text-decoration: underline; }
        .content { margin-bottom: 40px; text-align: justify; }
        .footer { margin-top: 60px; border-top: 1px solid #000; padding-top: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 10px; color: #66c; }
        .section-title { font-weight: bold; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <div class="title">LEGAL NOTICE</div>
    </div>

    <div class="date">Date: {{date}}</div>

    <div class="recipient">
        To,<br>
        The Manager / Authorized Officer,<br>
        <strong>{{company}}</strong>,<br>
        {{jurisdiction}} Commission Area
    </div>

    <div class="subject">
        Subject: Legal Notice under Section 2(11) / 2(47) of the Consumer Protection Act, 2019 regarding {{title}}.
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <p>Sir/Madam,</p>
        
        <p>Under instructions from my client <strong>{{consumerName}}</strong>, residing at {{consumerAddress}}, I hereby serve upon you the following notice:</p>

        <div class="section-title">1. FACTS OF THE MATTER:</div>
        <p>{{description}}</p>

        <div class="section-title">2. LEGAL GROUNDS:</div>
        <p>a) That the aforementioned acts constitute a clear "Deficiency in Service" under Section 2(11) of the Consumer Protection Act, 2019.</p>
        <p>b) That the failure to resolve my client's grievance constitutes an "Unfair Trade Practice" under Section 2(47) of the Act.</p>

        <div class="section-title">3. RELIEF SOUGHT:</div>
        <p>You are hereby called upon to:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Resolve the grievance mentioned above and refund/replace as applicable (Total Claim: ₹{{claimAmount}}).</li>
            <li>Provide compensation for mental agony and harassment caused to my client.</li>
            <li>Pay litigation costs towards this legal notice.</li>
        </ul>

        <p>You are hereby called upon to resolve this matter within <strong>15 days</strong> from receipt of this notice, failing which my client shall initiate legal proceedings under the Consumer Protection Act, 2019 before the appropriate District/State/National Consumer Commission.</p>

        <p>This is without prejudice to all other legal rights of my client.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="signature">
        Sincerely,<br><br>
        <strong>[Electronically Generated via CivilCOPZ]</strong><br>
        Legal Compliance Substrate v3.0
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        CivilCOPZ - Consumer Justice Operating System | Case ID: {{caseId}} | Timestamp: {{timestamp}}
    </div>
</body>
</html>
